      "description": "Drives @CircuitBreaker on BalanceService.getBalance. With the piggybank provider returning 503 (FAILING), repeated GET /api/v1/balance calls feed failures into the breaker's rolling window. Once it reaches requestVolumeThreshold=4 with failureRatio>=0.5, the breaker trips to OPEN: subsequent calls fast-fail with CircuitBreakerOpenException without touching the dependency. The OPEN-state check sets the provider back to HEALTHY and shows the call still fails (the breaker, not the dependency, is rejecting it). After the 3 second cool-down the breaker half-opens, a trial call succeeds, and it closes again."
    },
